&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Minimum opersting water pressure for Drippers: &#160;5 PSI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
