&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Use this dripper to slowly water a potted plant or landscapes using only 1 GPH of water. They are ergonomically designed with a wide-winged top to make the installation easier.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
