&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Install these drippers directly into the 1/2-in poly tubing by first snapping a hole using either of our punch tools (&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-hole-punch-tool-and-eight-goof-plugs&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLA-5&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-all-in-one-tool-makes-installation-easier&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLA-TOOL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;). Use our goof plugs if you snap a hole in the wrong place or want to relocate the dripper.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;These drippers can also be installed by running a piece of 1/4-in vinyl tubing to the plant from the 1/2-in poly tubing using the enclosed 1/4-in barbed couplers, then pushing in the dripper at the other end of the 1/4-in vinyl next to the plant.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff0000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Before installing the last dripper, turn on the water to allow a flow of water to clean out any debris that may have entered the line during installation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Our 1/4-in support stakes (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-one-quarter-inch-support-stakes-for-vinyl-and-drip-tubing&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLT-DST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) can be used to securely hold the 1/4-in vinyl tubing and 1 GPH dripper near the plant.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Also use our 1/4-in tees and elbows (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-one-quarter-inch-vinyl-tubing-connectors-tees-elbows&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLT-ATE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) to run the 1/4-in vinyl tubing in opposing directions or in tight corners to supply water to these drippers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
