&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We also recommend using our faucet filter (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://misterlandscaper.com/50-mesh-faucet-filter-for-micro-sprays-drippers&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLFF-41&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) with any drip system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;&quot;&gt;Drippers and Drip Tubing should NEVER be buried.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
