&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1/4-in Vinyl Tubing&lt;/strong&gt;&#160;- Run up to 100-ft of our 1/4-in Vinyl Tubing, installing up to&#160;13&#160;of these 1 GPH PC drippers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
