&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Water will steadily drip/flow out of either/or both of the 2 holes on opposing sides of the embedded dripper to give a total of .5 GPH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Tubing is bi-directional, meaning water can flow in either direction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
