&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Can be run directly from a faucet or from a 1/2-in poly tubing mainline&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;1/4-in In-Line Drip Tubing is great for all sorts of landscape applications, but it&#39;s particularly well suited for use in row gardens&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
