&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;However, for the more adventurous, this product is flexible enough to be snaked around landscapes, wrapped around trees, and customized in any number of ways&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
