&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;1/4-in In-Line Drip Tubing makes a great addition to any Mister Landscaper system and is an easy-to-install, self-contained drip irrigation solution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
