&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RECOMMENDATIONS &amp; LIMITATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We recommend this product be used with our Faucet Filter (&lt;a href=&quot;http://misterlandscaper.com/50-mesh-faucet-filter-for-micro-sprays-drippers&quot;&gt;MLFF-41&lt;/a&gt;)&#160;and &lt;a href=&quot;http://misterlandscaper.com/25-psi-regulator-drippers&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;25 PSI Pressure Regulator&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;With 25 PSI, a single run of 1/4-in in-line drip tubing can be no longer than&#160;50 feet&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;At 25 PSI, using 1/2-in poly tubing as the mainline, up to&#160;fifteen 33 foot lengths or up to ten 50 foot lengths of 1/4-in in-line drip tubing can be run off a single faucet&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;When using 1/4-in vinyl tubing as a lead to the 1/4-in in-line drip tubing, the length of the vinyl cannot exceed 15 feet&#160;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We do not&#160;recommend&#160;burying the 1/4-in in-line drip tubing, roots&#160;tend to grow towards the holes&#160;(water source).&#160; Also, dirt can clog the drippers in the tubing&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff0000; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Drippers and Drip Tubing should never be buried&lt;/span&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

