&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Use this flexible black 1/4-in vinyl tubing to extend Drippers and Micro-Spray Stake Assemblies further away from 1/2-in poly tubing.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
