&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This 1-Zone Automatic Water Timer is excellent for Easy, Hands Free, Automatic Watering.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Easy to set up and program. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Large LDC screen makes numbers easy to read.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Works with drip systems or sprinklers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Water flower beds, vegetable gardens, potted plants or automate a system for your bird bath! The possibilities are endless with this timer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;If rain is in the forecast, the Rain Delay feature will skip watering for up to 7 days with the simple push of a button. The timer will automatically resume watering after the&#160; rain delay has finished.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;Cycles can be up to 360 minutes (6 hours) in duration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;If you need to water manually to do a little extra watering, simply press the manual button. You can adjust the time up to 30 minutes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;Leak Proof Design.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;Runs up to 24 Cycles per day.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;Low Battery Indicator. (We recommend replacing batteries when the indicator reaches 20%).&#160; 2xAA&#160; alkaline batteries required (not included).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;7 Year Limited Warranty.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;Intended for &lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff0000;&quot;&gt;Outdoor Use Only&lt;/span&gt;.&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
