&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff0000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Before installing the last stake, besure to turn on the water and allow a flow of water to clean out any debris that may have entedered the line during installation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
