&lt;p&gt;&#160;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;When installing any irrigation system it is important to be aware of manufacturer recommendations and potential system limitations. Please be aware of the following:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;RECOMMENDATIONS&lt;/span&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We recommend using our 25 PSI Pressure Regulator (&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-25-psi-pressure-regulator-for-dripper-systems&quot;&gt;MLD-25PR&lt;/a&gt;) with any drip system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We also recommend using our faucet filter (&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-50-mesh-in-line-filter-with-three-quarter-inch-hose-threads&quot;&gt;MLFF-41&lt;/a&gt;) with any drip system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;When increasing the water output, be sure not to over rotate the top, as it can come off and become lost.&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff0000;&quot;&gt;Drippers and Drip Tubing should NEVER be buried.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MAXIMUM RUNS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1/4-in Vinyl Tubing&#160;&lt;/strong&gt;-&#160;Run up to 30-ft of our 1/4-in Vinyl Tubing, installing no more than eight (8) Adjustable Dripper Stakes set to &lt;em&gt;DRIP ONLY&lt;/em&gt;&#160;&lt;strong&gt;(Only 3 stakes can be used if set to wide open and maximum clicks using 10 GPH and small circle sprays)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1/2-in Poly&#160;Tubing&lt;/strong&gt; -&#160;Run up to 300-ft of our 1/2-in Poly Tubing, installing up to 30 of the Adjustable Dripper Stakes that are open to &lt;em&gt;full spray&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1/2-in&#160;Poly&#160;Tubing&lt;/strong&gt;&#160;-&#160;Run up to 300-ft of our 1/2-in Poly Tubing, installing up to 100 of the Adjustable Dripper Stakes with the top dialed down to &lt;em&gt;drip only&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Maximum operating pressure for Adjustable Drippers: &#160;15 PSI for Spraying 8 Streams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Minimum operating pressure for Adjustable Drippers: &#160;5 PSI for Dripping&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Each dripper is adjustable by turning the top dial to water from 0 to 10 GPH, releasing a flow ranging from drops of water up to spraying 8 individual streams of water in a 2.5-ft diameter spray pattern.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Use these adjustable drippers to gently water patio and potted plants or your landscapes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;A 25 PSI pressure regulator (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://misterlandscaper.com/25-psi-pressure-regulator-drippers&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLD-25PR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) and a faucet filter (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://misterlandscaper.com/150-mesh-faucet-filter-for-micro-sprays-drippers-2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLFF-41&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) are highly recommended to be used first at the water source when using these drippers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;These drippers can be installed directly into the 1/2-in poly tubing by first snapping a hole using either of our punch tools (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://misterlandscaper.com/hole-punch-toolgoof-plugs&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLA-51&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; ) or (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://misterlandscaper.com/all-in-one-tool-2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLA-TOOL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;).&#160; We recommend using the 1/2&quot; Poly Support stake(MLA-57) to hold the tubing in place.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;If you punch a hole in the wrong place or want to relocate the dripper, then simply remove it from the 1/2-in poly and snap in one of our goof plugs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;These drippers can also be installed by running a piece of 1/4-in vinyl tubing to the plant from the 1/2-in poly tubing using the enclosed 1/4-in barbed couplers then by pushing in the dripper at the other end of the 1/4-in vinyl next to the plant.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff0000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Before you end the line, turn on the water and allow the flow of water to clean out any debris&#160;that may have entered the line during installation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Our 1/4-in support stakes (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://misterlandscaper.com/14-in-vinyl-support-stake-qty-10&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLT-DST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) can be used to securely hold the 1/4-in vinyl and this adjustable dripper near the plant.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Also use our 1/4-in tees and elbows (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff; background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://misterlandscaper.com/14-in-combo-pack-teeselbowscouplers-qty-4-each&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff; background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;MLT-ATE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) to run the 1/4-in vinyl in opposing directions or in tight corners to supply water to these drippers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;display: inline !important;&quot;&gt;RECOMMENDATIONS&#160;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We recommend using our 25 PSI Pressure Regulator (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://misterlandscaper.com/25-psi-pressure-regulator-drippers&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLD-25PR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) with any drip system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We also recommend using our faucet filter (&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://misterlandscaper.com/150-mesh-faucet-filter-for-micro-sprays-drippers-2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3366ff;&quot;&gt;MLFF-41&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) with any drip system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;When increasing the water output, be sure not to over rotate the top, as it can come off and become lost.&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;&quot;&gt;Drippers and Drip Tubing should NEVER be buried.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
