&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Assembly includes a 13-in Stake, 27 inches of commercial-grade vinyl tubing, a 10 GPH Violet Flow Control, an On/Off Valve, and a Vinyl Collar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
