&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: left; margin: 0.8em 0px; font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #697629; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;RECOMMENDATIONS &amp; LIMITATIONS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; margin: 0.5em 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;When installing any irrigation system it is important to be aware of manufacturer recommendations and potential system limitations. Please be aware of the following:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We recommend using our 50 PSI Pressure Regulator (&lt;a style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot; href=&quot;/micro-spray-50-psi-pressure-regulator-for-micro-spray-systems&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff9900;&quot;&gt;MLA-58&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) with any micro spray system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We also recommend using one of our faucet filters (&lt;a style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot; href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-50-mesh-in-line-filter-with-three-quarter-inch-hose-threads&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff9900;&quot;&gt;MLFF-41&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;,&#160;&lt;a style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot; href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-150-mesh-in-line-filter-with-three-quarter-inch-hose-threads&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff9900;&quot;&gt;MLFF-150&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) for systems running on well water or hard water&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;At 40-50 PSI, no more than 50 Landscape Stake Assemblies can be run from a single outdoor faucet (300 linear feet of 1/2-in Poly Tubing is the maximum run length)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;If the Violet Flow Controllers are removed from a line of Landscape Stake Assemblies, water flow at the end of the line may be impaired&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
