&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;RECOMMENDATIONS &amp; LIMITATIONS&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;When installing any irrigation system it is important to be aware of manufacturer recommendations and potential system limitations. Please be aware of the following:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We recommend using our 50 PSI Pressure Regulator (&lt;a href=&quot;/micro-spray-50-psi-pressure-regulator-for-micro-spray-systems&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff9900;&quot;&gt;MLA-58&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) with any micro spray system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We also recommend using one of our faucet filters (&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-50-mesh-in-line-filter-with-three-quarter-inch-hose-threads&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff9900;&quot;&gt;MLFF-41&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-150-mesh-in-line-filter-with-three-quarter-inch-hose-threads&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff9900;&quot;&gt;MLFF-150&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) for systems running on well water or hard water&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;At 40-50 PSI, no more than 50 Landscape Stake Assemblies can be run from a single outdoor faucet (300 linear feet of 1/2-in Poly Tubing is the maximum run length)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;If the Violet Flow Controllers are removed from a line of Landscape Stake Assemblies, water flow at the end of the line may be impaired&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;If a Landscape Stake Assembly stops working, clean all the orifices using a cleaning tool (available on the &lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-all-in-one-tool-makes-installation-easier&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff9900;&quot;&gt;MLA-TOOL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) before replacing any parts. Often, restoring operation is simply a matter of clearing out debris from a clogged micro spray of flow controller&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Easy-to-use hole punch tool that makes holes in 1/2-in poly tubing to install Micro-Stake assemblies, drippers and 1/4-in couplers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Goof Plugs are included to seal up any punched holes made by mistake and unused holes in 1/2-in Poly Tubing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Goof Plugs are also used to end lines of 1/4-in Vinyl Tubing and 1/4-in In-Line Drip Tubing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The bright-orange color makes this punch tool easy to find if misplaced&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;(1 Tool / 8 Plugs Per Card)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;These&#160;Micro-Spray&#160;spinners rotate the water, giving a 360&#176; full-circle spray pattern with a diameter coverage up to 10 to 12 feet.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ideal to use this 360&#176; large-circle Micro-Sprinkler in the center of landscapes, flowerbeds, greenhouses, gardens and for large trees.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;When installed on top of our Mister-Riser assemblies (&lt;a href=&quot;/micro-spray-eight-and-a-half-inch-adjustable-riser&quot;&gt;MLS-231&lt;/a&gt;) or any of our Micro-Stake assemblies (&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-green-landscape-stake-assembly&quot;&gt;MLS-211&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/micro-spray-tan-landscape-stake-assembly&quot;&gt;MLS-TAN&lt;/a&gt;&#160;or &lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-black-landscape-stake-assembly&quot;&gt;MLS-BLA&lt;/a&gt;), this&#160;Micro-Spray&#160;will be flow-controlled to only use 10 GPH.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;If your water pressure is higher than 50 PSI, we suggest you use our 50 PSI pressure regulator (&lt;a href=&quot;/micro-spray-50-psi-pressure-regulator-for-micro-spray-systems&quot;&gt;MLA-58&lt;/a&gt;) at the beginning of the water source.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We highly suggest you use our faucet filter (&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-50-mesh-in-line-filter-with-three-quarter-inch-hose-threads&quot;&gt;MLFF-41&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-150-mesh-in-line-filter-with-three-quarter-inch-hose-threads&quot;&gt;MLFF-150&lt;/a&gt;) at the beginning of&#160; your water source if it comes from a well, pond or has debris.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This&#160;Micro-Spray&#160;is made with high-quality UV-inhibited resins that are made to last for years in extreme weather conditions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
