&lt;h2&gt;&#160;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;RECOMMENDATIONS &amp; LIMITATIONS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;When installing any irrigation system it is important to be aware of manufacturer recommendations and potential system limitations. Please be aware of the following:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; min-height: 14px; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We recommend using our 25 PSI Pressure Regulator (&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-25-psi-pressure-regulator-for-dripper-systems&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff9900;&quot;&gt;MLD-25PR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) with any system using 1/4-in vinyl as the main line&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We also recommend using our faucet filter (&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-50-mesh-in-line-filter-with-three-quarter-inch-hose-threads&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff9900;&quot;&gt;MLFF-41&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) for systems running on hard water or well water&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Due to limited water flow through 1/4-in Vinyl Tubing, for full function, no more than one kit (8 Pot Stakes) can be installed on a faucet&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;To run up to 65 Pot Stakes from a single outdoor faucet, 1/2-in Poly Tubing must first be installed as the main line.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; min-height: 14px; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;If a Micro Spray Pot Stake stops working, twist and remove the spray head to clean the spray orifice. Use the included cleaning tool to remove any debris.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; min-height: 14px; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;A Favorite! The pot stake features a 2-ft radius 165&#176; half-circle fan down-spray pattern.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The pot stakes are easy to position with a built in arrow to set depth and direction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The spray distance can be adjusted down with the On/Off Valve to a much smaller size.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;To end a line of Pot Stakes, simply run a line of 1/4-in Vinyl from the last Tee Fitting to the final Pot Stake.&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Depending on water pressure, Pot Stakes may use 3.5 – 7.5 gph.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;3 - 1/4-in Couplers (&lt;a href=&quot;/drip-irrigation-micro-spray-one-quarter-inch-barb-and-barb-couplers&quot;&gt;MLT-BXB&lt;/a&gt;) are with this product for installing 1/4-in Vinyl tubing to the 1/2-in Poly Tubing.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
