&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Use the extender to increase spray coverage in large pots and planter boxes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
