&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;If your water pressure is higher than 50 PSI, we suggest you use our 50 PSI pressure regulator (&lt;a href=&quot;/micro-spray-50-psi-pressure-regulator-for-micro-spray-systems&quot;&gt;MLA-58&lt;/a&gt;) at the beginning of the water source.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
